contributor: Roberts, Don, 1938-2022|Griscom, Richard|Marjorie Iglow Mitchell Multimedia Center|Northwestern University (Evanston, Ill.). Library
description: Interview with NU music librarian Don Roberts on the occasion of his retirement. He discusses his life and career including his youth, early years at NU, developing the Music Library as a collection of distinction, memories of other library staff, and work with the Music Library Association and International Association of Music Libraries.|Recorded September 27, 2002.
